    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WELCOME TO THE LAND OF FOOT</h2><br>Here the shoes are in control, and humans are nothing but tools.<br><br>Waking up, you are struck by the terrible news that your sole mate is missing!<br>Pretty soon, you come to notice that you are far from alone since everybody in the Land Of Foot is suddenly missing their partner.<br>This is the start of a crazy journey leading you on a mission to figure out what has happened and fix it.<br><br>Gather your friends and join the adventure, work together and fight your way through evil boots and bosses.<br>Use your lace to solve puzzles and win battles; a skilled player will soon learn how to do more than bunny ears.<br>Level up by finding shields and weapons, and they will help you bring your sole mate home from the evil Peg Leg, a bitter old wooden leg. <br><br>So, put the sole in soul and work together in this goofy world.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808380/extras/cc139158690ec22eff7142dc394641c4.webp?t=1704477328\" width=600 height=2 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808380/extras/3409ff5bde9dbd4021284eca1fcd3d46.poster.avif?t=1704477328\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808380/extras/3409ff5bde9dbd4021284eca1fcd3d46.webm?t=1704477328\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808380/extras/3409ff5bde9dbd4021284eca1fcd3d46.mp4?t=1704477328\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >KEY FEATURES</h2>",
